{"tid":782852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【火上加油】指解放軍為長程戰機配核彈 美國防部報告：似進行攻擊美國訓練","createTime":"2018-08-17T05:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T05:29:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1090d712a92dae5a8be1f73f7c0750c3d1e875bc","tid":782852,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180817/large/1534464787_3805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180817%2Flarge%2F1534464787_3805.jpg&h=1571e35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部周四發表報告稱，中國空軍轟炸機近年活動增加，似乎正進行針對美國及其盟友的攻擊訓練，解放軍亦正為長程戰機配備核彈，預料10年內可以投入行動。<br />\n<br />\n五角大廈在周年報告中說，在過去3年，解放軍急速擴大轟炸機的活動範圍、增強在關鍵近海地區的經驗及可能進行針對美國及其盟友的攻擊訓練。報告特別強調中國正加強全球影響力，並估計中國去年軍費超過1900億美元(1.48萬億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n報告說，解放軍繼續擴張行動，「超出展示軍力改善的目的」但暫未清楚北京政府想表達甚麼信息。<br />\n<br />\n中美目前因貿易糾紛而關係緊張，雙方代表正打算進行貿易談判，謀求令關稅糾紛降溫，避免爆發全面貿易戰。中國駐美大使館未對報告置評。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"c44d5a8d505e95ec3a827e85c292a408847a7c65","tid":782852,"uid":13102,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/135523_0b055f0607c6d1767eb541acdc04e9f8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F135523_0b055f0607c6d1767eb541acdc04e9f8.gif&h=8de00178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fd7d2c7c75c4262bb377f9c72a3c6549cfa7044","tid":782852,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0e9175c59516e6f416e2b96d043f201e27066c","tid":782852,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/232302_2ef04438b59f91171acb56df8b69dd75.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F232302_2ef04438b59f91171acb56df8b69dd75.gif&h=69416c3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb1baacddf0f5a0d23022de737e6009192025352","tid":782852,"uid":120678,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<br />\n支那戰機轟炸機未出第一島鏈就被人打左落黎<br />\n仲狂言轟炸美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d819af19f3457db735ee6b0243e8cc6872678e","tid":782852,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"取代蘇聯搞海陸空核力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058cd21fe1a2baeeafa32f46e995d980c856673f","tid":782852,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdf947b638a70d4063799b0094da61ca37f3e05","tid":782852,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"786f9aef783c5a970cf020c70a798c8b2dd6e736","tid":782852,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"前蘇聯亡國之路"},{"pid":"166e04d04bf03f7a158e2302477dd07f726eb9a1","tid":782852,"uid":63154,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"戰機攜帶核彈頭飛到遠一遠，唔會係防務需要啦，有咩好講"},{"pid":"fdf2882078c614482ea8a8bd79d3131265cedce0","tid":782852,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"bfdf947b638a70d4063799b0094da61ca37f3e05","tid":782852,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"你唔發展軍備